## 🎨 React Native Reanimated

### Animated Values
```typescript
import Animated, {
  useAnimatedStyle,
  useSharedValue,
  withSpring,
  withTiming,
} from 'react-native-reanimated';

const MyComponent = () => {
  const opacity = useSharedValue(1);
  const translateX = useSharedValue(0);

  const animatedStyle = useAnimatedStyle(() => ({
    opacity: opacity.value,
    transform: [{ translateX: translateX.value }],
  }));

  const handlePress = () => {
    opacity.value = withTiming(0.5);
    translateX.value = withSpring(100);
  };

  return (
    <Animated.View className="flex-1 items-center" style={animatedStyle}>
      <Text className="text-foreground">Animated Content</Text>
    </Animated.View>
  );
};
```

> **Note:** Use `className` for static styles and `style` (via `useAnimatedStyle`) only for dynamic/animated values.

### Layout Animations
```typescript
import { Layout, FadeIn, FadeOut } from 'react-native-reanimated';

<Animated.View
  className="card"
