## 🚫 Common Mistakes to Avoid

### ❌ DON'T
```typescript
// Don't use any
const data: any = fetchData();

// Don't use StyleSheet.create()
const styles = StyleSheet.create({ container: { flex: 1 } });

// Don't use inline styles
<View style={{ flex: 1, padding: 16 }} />

// Don't use inline functions in render
<Pressable onPress={() => doSomething()} />

// Don't use FlatList for long lists
<FlatList data={items} />

// Don't use var
var count = 0;

// Don't use console.log in production
console.log('Debug info');
```

### ✅ DO
```typescript
// Use proper types
const data: UserData = fetchData();

// Use Uniwind className
<View className="flex-1 p-4 bg-background" />

// Use useCallback
const handlePress = useCallback(() => doSomething(), []);

// Use FlashList
<FlashList data={items} estimatedItemSize={100} />

// Use const/let
const count = 0;

// Use Sentry for logging
Sentry.captureException(error);
```

